{"title":"【076】CSS背景滚动视觉差","slug":"hell0-world22","date":"2022-10-17T13:28:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:18:54.778Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world22.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                css 视觉差案例    div.box*3回车快速添加带有不同类名的div元素","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>css 视觉差案例</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    div.box*3回车快速添加带有不同类名的div元素<span id=\"more\"></span>。<br><br>\n    css中通配符*下添加magin,padding,都为0，消除元素默认内外边距<br><br>\n    一定要设置祖父元素的高度如html,body：height: 100%;<br><br>\n    代码简写时，background-size后要先添加位置，若没有指定位置就添加0px空格0px,再添加cover之类<br><br>\n    <div class=\"box1\"></div>\n    <div class=\"box2\"></div>\n    <div class=\"box3\"></div>   \n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}